

## Area Assessments
Area assessments are an excellent start point for understanding an operating environment. Possible outputs include:
  + Understanding area atmospherics
  + Identify threat actors
  + Establish social pattern-of-life for an area
  + Learn the physical terrain
  + Learn the human terrain

## Method

### Strategic
  + Geopolitical considerations
  + Demographic understanding
  + Cultural, social, and religious, considerations

## Assessment

### Area Overview
  + Maps
  + Country Information and Incidents

### Local News Topics and Trends
  + local sources

### SocInt
  + TweetDeck
  + Trends Map
  + Tweet maps
  + Social Geo Lens

